# Why Broker Instead of Direct REST?

Without Kafka

```
Order

↓

Payment

↓

Inventory

↓

Notification
```

Every service must know every other service.

With Kafka

```
Order

↓

Kafka

↓

Payment

Inventory

Notification

Analytics
```

Order only knows Kafka.

Nothing else.

This reduces coupling.

